title: Gluten Free & More - April/May 2016
description:
English | 92 Pages | PDF | 21.6 Mb

Gluten Free & More magazine is THE magazine for people with allergies and food sensitivities.

Every new issue and digital back issue of Gluten Free and More Magazine features delicious recipes, diet advice and invaluable medical information:
Gluten-free and dairy-free recipes
Allergy-friendly restaurant guidance
The latest allergy research
Questions for your allergist and doctor
Expert advice on kids' allergies
Gluten-Free resources and support
New gluten-free food products
And much more!
